From 8af23b4d571675aa78b6a4669c8ef3582da8b33e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jake Teton-Landis <just.1.jake@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 15:07:32 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Protocol tests for the signal-scheduler bridge

Pins: pinned-lane dispatches across separate events land in one commit;
unpinned claims stay per-event; pass starts and per-root commit reports carry
(root, lanes); the mutation window brackets exactly React's DOM mutation
phase (layout effects outside); isRendering/getWorkInProgress introspection;
flushSync excludes pinned-lane work.
---
 .../__tests__/ReactDOMSignalScheduler-test.js | 238 ++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 238 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 packages/react-dom/src/__tests__/ReactDOMSignalScheduler-test.js

diff --git a/packages/react-dom/src/__tests__/ReactDOMSignalScheduler-test.js b/packages/react-dom/src/__tests__/ReactDOMSignalScheduler-test.js
new file mode 100644
index 0000000000..763dd3c7a5
--- /dev/null
+++ b/packages/react-dom/src/__tests__/ReactDOMSignalScheduler-test.js
@@ -0,0 +1,238 @@
+/**
